{"tid":1750760,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"星期一黎明行動去撚咗邊","createTime":"2019-11-24T13:33:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-28T14:33:56.000Z","uid":295585,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"52bcd72bbdf81204489beaac45b1725c97e1d024","tid":1750760,"uid":295585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T13:33:42.000Z","msg":"屌你老母正苦春袋"},{"pid":"e71fb944a4f3d1654d9bea8a83248ea2482a10b6","tid":1750760,"uid":202464,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T13:35:28.000Z","msg":"連登太多飯民打手<br />\n<br />\n佢地做乜既目的都只係為選舉<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n選舉一完就走晒去架啦"},{"pid":"47bd026ccc02b21f3e5ffe29b674555c22257d9f","tid":1750760,"uid":276382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T13:36:19.000Z","msg":"26/11 全城樂手齊心演奏薈通利<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1748620\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1748620</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n黃店與藍店之間總有綠店，不表態、裝作中立。 我們沒有必要跟中共一樣，迫每間公司歸邊。既然深藍老闆要扮作政治中立，就不要以為滅聲、不談政治就是中立，事實是容不下員工的反對聲音。<br />\n<br />\n平日琴行歡迎客人、甚至員工試玩樂器，既然琴行要賺黃絲Band 仔的錢，就不應該對他們彈奏《願榮光歸香港》不滿。如不歡迎黃絲客人，罵他們做「曱甴」，不如叫手足直接將琴行加盟藍店。<br />\n<br />\n用音樂感化「偽綠店」，號召各樂手一同到琴行試玩樂器，齊齊演奏《願榮光歸香港》。<br />\n不會樂器的朋友歡迎一起詠唱或當樂迷。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n全城樂手齊心演奏薈通利<br />\n日期：2019年11月26日（星期二）<br />\n時間：7:30pm<br />\n地點：尖沙咀通利琴行<br />\n衣著：做返自己 （宜戴口罩防二噁英）<br />\n大會指定歌曲：《願榮光歸香港》<br />\n<br />\n結他譜下載：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.guitarians.com/chord/76287/香港人-願榮光歸香港\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.guitarians.com%2Fchord%2F76287%2F%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA-%E9%A1%98%E6%A6%AE%E5%85%89%E6%AD%B8%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF&d=8H50EXT8eKO%2B303r5eJ0KCaGrLhPWbn%2F%2Bskqqi57m1s%3D&h=deb6e09b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.guitarians.com/chord/76287/香港人-願榮光歸香港</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7MwV9Jf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7MwV9Jf.jpg&h=68035d32&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d213a4cc38abe2175a301a0a1c1120973d5cfc49","tid":1750760,"uid":295585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T13:36:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f486d089cf8cfcb3600f3a880565b3a6c1c09931","tid":1750760,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T16:05:04.000Z","msg":"經過區選休息風 如不重整黎明行動及工會三罷路線 運動將在短期內降溫消亡<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/aojpxOU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/aojpxOU</a>"},{"pid":"26bb39ac26f1a5cef29654519a8547584a57cd4c","tid":1750760,"uid":117896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T16:06:21.000Z","msg":"鄧炳強上任 社會就回復正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd4415785d5077282d7e5a69fe1712d00351fcf5","tid":1750760,"uid":150625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T19:47:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98aa4f793b0d08e20001b4bac441383721bcd51e","tid":1750760,"uid":337318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T19:56:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"507f59ea089d9d88fc66e6af81eb0022a638daee","tid":1750760,"uid":295585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T14:33:56.000Z","msg":"屌"}],"pinned":{"pid":"26bb39ac26f1a5cef29654519a8547584a57cd4c","tid":1750760,"uid":117896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T16:06:21.000Z","msg":"鄧炳強上任 社會就回復正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}}